<subSubSection pageId="25" pageNumber="26" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="25.[533,1535,276,856]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[565,669,520,544]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Remarks:</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authorityName="K. Andersen" authorityYear="1908" box="[676,750,519,544]" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Pteropus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="lylei">
<emphasis box="[676,696,520,543]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">H</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[708,750,519,543]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">lylei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was once considered to be conspecific with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1891" box="[1215,1304,520,544]" class="Mammalia" family="Hipposideridae" genus="Hipposideros" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="pratti">
<emphasis box="[1215,1235,520,543]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">H</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[1247,1304,520,543]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">pratti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
[
<bibRefCitation author="Ellerman JR &amp; Morrison-Scott TCS" box="[1320,1358,520,544]" journalOrPublisher="London: Trustees of the British Museum (Natural History)" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" pagination="1966" refId="ref43528" refString="138. Ellerman JR, Morrison-Scott TCS. Checklist of Palaearctic and Indian Mammals 1758 to 1946, 2 nd Ed. London: Trustees of the British Museum (Natural History); 1966." title="Checklist of Palaearctic and Indian Mammals 1758 to 1946" type="book" year="1913">138</bibRefCitation>
]. Although Tate [
<bibRefCitation author="Tate GHH" box="[542,580,554,578]" journalOrPublisher="The Macmillan Company, New York" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" refId="ref43564" refString="139. Tate GHH. Mammals of Eastern Asia. The Macmillan Company, New York; 1947." title="Mammals of Eastern Asia" type="book" year="1947">139</bibRefCitation>
] commented that 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1891" box="[776,865,554,578]" class="Mammalia" family="Hipposideridae" genus="Hipposideros" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="pratti">
<emphasis box="[776,796,555,578]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">H</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[808,865,555,578]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">pratti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is known from mountainous parts of lower Peninsular 
<collectingCountry name="Malaysia" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Malaysia</collectingCountry>
, we could not find any other records of the species in Peninsular 
<collectingCountry box="[1252,1349,589,613]" name="Malaysia" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Malaysia</collectingCountry>
. Consequently, we did not include 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1891" box="[737,825,624,648]" class="Mammalia" family="Hipposideridae" genus="Hipposideros" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="pratti">
<emphasis box="[737,757,624,647]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">H</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[768,825,624,647]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">pratti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in this checklist.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="25.[533,1535,276,856]" box="[565,870,658,682]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[565,710,658,682]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">IUCN status:</emphasis>
